1
00:00:44,477 --> 00:00:48,114
Tao Sor now knows, that he's not my real brother!

2
00:00:50,550 --> 00:00:53,653
I have to do everything to make him forget,

3
00:00:54,320 --> 00:00:56,189
and come back to being the Tao Sor I know!

4
00:00:56,589 --> 00:00:58,725
Why do you have to go this far?

5
00:00:59,325 --> 00:01:00,827
I'm protecting you.

6
00:01:01,561 --> 00:01:02,629
That's not true.

7
00:01:03,563 --> 00:01:05,365
Both you and Mom know well, don't you?

8
00:01:08,468 --> 00:01:09,769
Kim..

9
00:01:11,471 --> 00:01:12,572
where are you?

10
00:01:14,374 --> 00:01:15,575
Come see me.

11
00:01:17,477 --> 00:01:19,345
I'm waiting on the bridge.

12
00:01:20,814 --> 00:01:22,215
Okay, alright.

13
00:01:22,749 --> 00:01:23,883
I'll hurry there.

14
00:01:24,451 --> 00:01:25,652
Wait for me, Tao Sor.

15
00:01:26,252 --> 00:01:27,287
Wait for me.

16
00:01:27,353 --> 00:01:31,558
I thought I was dead, but I was able to wake up.

17
00:01:31,991 --> 00:01:35,361
Then I found out that I've been Sleeping Beauty for over 3 years.

18
00:01:35,361 --> 00:01:37,197
And your son and boyfriend?

19
00:01:37,197 --> 00:01:40,166
My husband lost his life at sea,

20
00:01:40,166 --> 00:01:44,704
as for my son, he was swallowed by the sea, disappearing without a trace.

21
00:01:44,704 --> 00:01:47,040
At first, I couldn't take it.

22
00:01:47,407 --> 00:01:49,008
I tried to find him,

23
00:01:49,342 --> 00:01:52,846
but the officers said it's already been 3 years.

24
00:01:53,113 --> 00:01:56,149
If they could, then they would have already found him.

25
00:01:56,382 --> 00:02:00,053
The boy that this woman is talking about is me?

26
00:02:00,587 --> 00:02:01,187
Yes.

27
00:02:02,055 --> 00:02:04,090
I'm not sure either, but I think so.

28
00:02:05,125 --> 00:02:06,960
So we have hurry and get you to see her.

29
00:02:07,627 --> 00:02:12,232
I promised you, that I would help you find your real mom.

30
00:02:23,543 --> 00:02:24,410
Don't answer.

31
00:02:25,278 --> 00:02:27,046
Let me take you to see your other first,

32
00:02:28,515 --> 00:02:30,283
and then I'll tell you everything.

33
00:02:48,801 --> 00:02:49,769
This way!

34
00:02:55,375 --> 00:02:56,342
We have to got there!

35
00:03:11,224 --> 00:03:12,892
Tao Sor.

36
00:03:14,027 --> 00:03:15,628
I think...

37
00:03:17,864 --> 00:03:20,867
we didn't make it.

38
00:03:23,203 --> 00:03:24,103
So...

39
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:28,308
What should we do, Kim?

40
00:04:49,989 --> 00:04:52,558
I'm..sorry.

41
00:04:53,126 --> 00:04:56,095
For not being able to find your real mom like I promised.

42
00:05:00,700 --> 00:05:02,001
Don't worry.

43
00:05:03,102 --> 00:05:04,304
From now on,

44
00:05:05,071 --> 00:05:07,106
I'll take care of you.

45
00:05:11,044 --> 00:05:12,312
Thank you.

46
00:05:13,780 --> 00:05:16,182
Why are you thanking me? We're dating, after all.

47
00:05:25,191 --> 00:05:28,194
Let's...go get your things from your house.

48
00:05:35,168 --> 00:05:37,303
How's it going, Talay?

49
00:05:39,539 --> 00:05:40,840
He turbed off his phone.

50
00:05:41,274 --> 00:05:44,477
He looks tired, he might faint somewhere.

51
00:05:46,179 --> 00:05:48,314
I think I should go look for him myself.

52
00:05:48,748 --> 00:05:49,982
Talay, stay with mom.

53
00:05:50,183 --> 00:05:51,150
Calm down, Dad.

54
00:05:52,552 --> 00:05:53,720
He'll be back.

55
00:06:05,164 --> 00:06:06,232
It's you again?

56
00:06:07,066 --> 00:06:08,468
Where'd you take Tao Sor?!

57
00:06:08,701 --> 00:06:10,703
When will you leave Tao Sor's life?

58
00:06:11,003 --> 00:06:12,238
Probably too late now, man.

59
00:06:12,905 --> 00:06:15,875
Because Tao Sor's promised, that he'll stay with me.

60
00:06:18,277 --> 00:06:20,279
Tao Sor, come to Mommy!

61
00:06:20,513 --> 00:06:21,280
Mom?

62
00:06:21,848 --> 00:06:24,817
Just now, I went to go see my mom with Kim.

63
00:06:27,286 --> 00:06:28,121
Hey, Kim.

64
00:06:28,988 --> 00:06:30,523
What lies have you feeding Tao Sor?

65
00:06:30,623 --> 00:06:32,058
I just told him the truth.

66
00:06:32,458 --> 00:06:33,359
Another thing...

67
00:06:33,526 --> 00:06:36,496
he's promised with me that he'll stay with me.

68
00:06:37,397 --> 00:06:38,164
Let's go pack your things.

69
00:06:38,564 --> 00:06:39,665
Look, Tao Sor...

70
00:06:41,801 --> 00:06:42,869
Don't listen to him.

71
00:06:43,736 --> 00:06:45,204
You are my brother.

72
00:06:45,671 --> 00:06:47,073
and these are your parents!

73
00:06:47,473 --> 00:06:48,808
If you don't believe me...

74
00:06:50,543 --> 00:06:51,544
take a look at this.

75
00:06:53,679 --> 00:06:55,047
It's a picture of our family.

76
00:06:55,348 --> 00:06:56,749
Even if you don't remember,

77
00:06:56,949 --> 00:06:58,117
these memories...

78
00:06:58,418 --> 00:06:59,886
hold so much meaning to us.

79
00:07:00,086 --> 00:07:02,822
Tao Sor, you will always be my son.

80
00:07:02,822 --> 00:07:04,056
Don't leave.

81
00:07:04,791 --> 00:07:05,525
Tao Sor.

82
00:07:06,526 --> 00:07:08,394
He's only known you for a few months,

83
00:07:08,795 --> 00:07:10,763
he only thinks about his own needs.

84
00:07:11,764 --> 00:07:13,065
He doesn't care about what you need.

85
00:07:13,399 --> 00:07:14,200
Not true!

86
00:07:14,634 --> 00:07:16,936
Everything I said has been the truth.

87
00:07:17,203 --> 00:07:19,305
And I also want Tao Sor to live his own life.

88
00:07:19,439 --> 00:07:21,607
Not accept that he's just a person you took in.

89
00:07:23,309 --> 00:07:24,577
Tao Sor, let's go.

90
00:07:24,877 --> 00:07:25,344
Tao Sor.

91
00:07:28,781 --> 00:07:29,549
That's enough, Talay.

92
00:07:30,516 --> 00:07:31,918
If you really love Tao Sor,

93
00:07:32,418 --> 00:07:34,086
you'd want him to have his own life.

94
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:35,288
Just this...

95
00:07:36,022 --> 00:07:37,990
you've already ruined his life far enough.

96
00:07:37,990 --> 00:07:39,525
You're the one that needs to get out.

97
00:07:39,592 --> 00:07:41,394
You have to get out of our lives.

98
00:07:42,495 --> 00:07:43,696
We were doing fine,

99
00:07:44,297 --> 00:07:45,698
but you came and messed with everything.

100
00:07:45,698 --> 00:07:46,766
I will leave!

101
00:07:47,433 --> 00:07:48,668
but Tao Sor's coming with me.

102
00:07:49,435 --> 00:07:50,803
tao Sor's not going anywhere.

103
00:07:50,803 --> 00:07:52,104
This is his home,

104
00:07:52,605 --> 00:07:53,840
his family....

105
00:07:54,841 --> 00:07:56,242
Tao Sor, come with me.

106
00:07:56,342 --> 00:07:57,176
Tao Sor leaves with me!

107
00:07:57,276 --> 00:07:58,444
You're the one that needs to leave.

108
00:07:59,178 --> 00:08:00,446
But Tao Sor's agreed with me.

109
00:08:00,646 --> 00:08:02,281
Tao Sor's decided to go with me!

110
00:08:02,281 --> 00:08:02,982
Tao Sor, stay with me.

111
00:08:02,982 --> 00:08:04,383
That's enough!

112
00:08:09,522 --> 00:08:11,824
I don't know who to trust anymore!

113
00:08:14,961 --> 00:08:16,629
Tao Sor, don't go anywhere!

114
00:08:17,196 --> 00:08:18,064
Tao Sor!

115
00:08:18,264 --> 00:08:19,499
I'll go after him, Mom.

116
00:08:20,900 --> 00:08:21,767
Tao Sor!

117
00:09:08,114 --> 00:09:08,948
Tao Sor!

118
00:09:09,515 --> 00:09:10,349
Tao Sor!

119
00:09:11,217 --> 00:09:12,084
Tao Sor!

120
00:09:12,485 --> 00:09:13,319
Tao Sor!

121
00:09:13,986 --> 00:09:14,820
Tao Sor!

122
00:09:17,523 --> 00:09:18,357
Tao Sor!

123
00:09:20,192 --> 00:09:21,193
Tao Sor, pleae don't be hurt.

124
00:09:25,565 --> 00:09:27,300
Tao Sor! Can you hear me?

125
00:09:30,736 --> 00:09:31,938
I love you, Tao Sor!

126
00:09:43,583 --> 00:09:44,684
You'll be fine, okay?

127
00:10:21,220 --> 00:10:22,121
Kim.

128
00:10:24,056 --> 00:10:25,725
When will you understand?

129
00:10:28,527 --> 00:10:31,497
Every time he finds out the truth, he turns out like this.

130
00:10:33,499 --> 00:10:36,502
You might think I'm selfish for lying to Tao Sor.

131
00:10:38,270 --> 00:10:41,641
But what good comes from him finding out the truth?

132
00:10:45,711 --> 00:10:47,580
Before you met Tao Sor,

133
00:10:49,015 --> 00:10:51,517
it wasn't like this situation never happened.

134
00:10:54,153 --> 00:10:56,188
In the end, when Tao Sor wakes up.

135
00:10:58,524 --> 00:11:00,459
everything just disappears.

136
00:11:01,827 --> 00:11:03,663
There's just me and my family

137
00:11:04,697 --> 00:11:06,565
who still remember everything.

138
00:11:23,749 --> 00:11:26,752
I beg you, don't tak Tao Sor away from us.

139
00:11:43,602 --> 00:11:45,738
Our family has been broken up enough.

140
00:11:45,905 --> 00:11:47,873
Ever since Tao Sor left.

141
00:11:48,841 --> 00:11:51,077
But him coming back today...

142
00:11:51,644 --> 00:11:54,947
is like a reward for all of us.

143
00:12:01,153 --> 00:12:01,954
Tao Sor...

144
00:12:03,222 --> 00:12:05,324
is important to all of us.

145
00:12:17,303 --> 00:12:20,306
I ask of you, please return Tao Sor to us.

146
00:12:29,348 --> 00:12:31,083
I understand everyone's feelings.

147
00:12:33,185 --> 00:12:34,987
How losing someone can hurt so much.

148
00:12:35,721 --> 00:12:36,856
I also...

149
00:12:37,523 --> 00:12:40,526
lost a brother 10 years ago.

150
00:12:43,629 --> 00:12:46,632
But I've never thought of replacing him.

151
00:12:47,967 --> 00:12:49,568
Because in reality,

152
00:12:50,436 --> 00:12:53,439
no one can really replace anyone else.

153
00:12:57,109 --> 00:13:00,112
Please don't! Don't take Tao Sor away from me!

154
00:13:01,380 --> 00:13:03,082
Don't take Tao Sor away from us.

155
00:13:04,350 --> 00:13:05,351
Mom...

156
00:13:06,519 --> 00:13:09,522
Mom, get up.

157
00:13:16,195 --> 00:13:19,198
Dad, take Mom to go rest.

158
00:13:20,432 --> 00:13:21,967
Take care of your brother.

159
00:14:15,087 --> 00:14:16,522
What does his condition look like?

160
00:14:17,022 --> 00:14:18,724
His body is just exhausted,

161
00:14:19,225 --> 00:14:21,227
like he's been avoiding sleep for several days.

162
00:14:21,727 --> 00:14:23,362
Plus, he has face a stressful situation,

163
00:14:23,863 --> 00:14:25,598
so his body couldn't take it.

164
00:14:26,298 --> 00:14:30,269
But I gave him some meds and gave him an IV, he should be fine soon.

165
00:14:32,037 --> 00:14:33,038
So will this...

166
00:14:33,706 --> 00:14:35,808
have any effect on his memories?

167
00:14:39,578 --> 00:14:41,714
The brain didn't recieve any trauma,

168
00:14:42,381 --> 00:14:44,083
but in the case of memories...

169
00:14:44,617 --> 00:14:46,151
we'll have to take another look when he wakes up.

170
00:14:47,219 --> 00:14:49,221
He might remember everything.

171
00:14:49,955 --> 00:14:51,023
Or...

172
00:14:52,258 --> 00:14:53,759
he might not remember anything,

173
00:14:54,326 --> 00:14:55,928
like how you wanted.

174
00:15:01,967 --> 00:15:03,402
I'm asking seriously,

175
00:15:04,603 --> 00:15:05,638
Don't you get tired?

176
00:15:06,038 --> 00:15:07,039
Of course I do.

177
00:15:08,507 --> 00:15:09,708
But I have to do it.

178
00:15:11,977 --> 00:15:14,113
It's really the best thing for everyone.

179
00:15:24,623 --> 00:15:26,525
If you're tired, you should get some rest.

180
00:15:27,860 --> 00:15:29,361
Thank you so much.

181
00:15:31,897 --> 00:15:33,299
For never leaving me.

182
00:15:53,352 --> 00:15:54,520
You guys...

183
00:15:56,789 --> 00:15:59,358
why isn't everyone asleep?

184
00:16:00,759 --> 00:16:02,328
We were waiting for you.

185
00:16:03,262 --> 00:16:05,364
How was it? Did you see her?

186
00:16:08,300 --> 00:16:12,271
It's okay. I'll find a way to contact her.

187
00:16:12,671 --> 00:16:16,642
No matter what, Tao Sor has to be able to met his real mother.

188
00:16:17,643 --> 00:16:18,577
I think...

189
00:16:20,746 --> 00:16:21,680
you don't have to.

190
00:16:22,648 --> 00:16:25,617
Why are you sighing like that?

191
00:16:32,224 --> 00:16:33,325
Sometimes...

192
00:16:35,060 --> 00:16:37,363
him not being able to remember...

193
00:16:39,164 --> 00:16:41,367
could be a good thing for Tao Sor.

194
00:16:43,469 --> 00:16:44,203
And...

195
00:16:45,304 --> 00:16:47,706
you're gonna just let him forget you so easily?

196
00:16:51,844 --> 00:16:54,847
I'm only here for a year,

197
00:16:55,114 --> 00:16:58,117
I don't see why I have to get attached to anyone.

198
00:17:03,589 --> 00:17:06,592
And can you really forget him, Kim?

199
00:17:24,710 --> 00:17:25,944
Hey.

200
00:17:26,845 --> 00:17:30,682
If you want to cry, just let it out. You don't have to be strong all the time.

201
00:17:39,058 --> 00:17:40,726
Wrong person!

202
00:17:41,060 --> 00:17:42,127
It's not wrong.

203
00:17:42,928 --> 00:17:44,063
It's the same for you.

204
00:17:44,696 --> 00:17:46,432
You don't have to be strong all the time.

205
00:17:46,799 --> 00:17:50,135
You can show some weakness, I won't tell anyone.

206
00:17:56,542 --> 00:17:59,545
To be honest, sometimes...

207
00:18:00,646 --> 00:18:03,816
you don't have to keep forgetting about him.

208
00:18:05,984 --> 00:18:07,786
It's not even your fault.

209
00:18:09,188 --> 00:18:11,056
No one wants things like this to happen.

210
00:18:14,793 --> 00:18:17,796
We should just the remember the good moments,

211
00:18:18,097 --> 00:18:19,898
don't let anyone take those memories away.

212
00:18:26,305 --> 00:18:27,739
I love you, Sang.

213
00:18:29,508 --> 00:18:31,510
I love you too, Kim.

214
00:18:34,780 --> 00:18:37,783
I also love the both of you.

215
00:20:07,339 --> 00:20:08,941
Tao Sor.

216
00:20:13,378 --> 00:20:15,080
Who are you?

217
00:20:17,816 --> 00:20:19,418
What is this place?

218
00:20:19,985 --> 00:20:20,986
And...

219
00:20:22,154 --> 00:20:23,155
who am I?

220
00:20:23,522 --> 00:20:24,856
Your name is Tao Sor.

221
00:20:25,757 --> 00:20:27,359
You're my little brother.

222
00:20:28,627 --> 00:20:30,262
I don't remember that?

223
00:20:39,304 --> 00:20:40,439
It's okay.

224
00:20:42,507 --> 00:20:44,376
It's good that you don't remember.

225
00:21:55,914 --> 00:21:58,917
Hello, Chef Mochi. I'm Daiji.

226
00:22:02,988 --> 00:22:03,955
Oh...

227
00:22:05,390 --> 00:22:06,958
Talay's told me already.

228
00:22:07,693 --> 00:22:08,627
Really?

229
00:22:09,394 --> 00:22:10,529
What did he say?

230
00:22:11,596 --> 00:22:12,931
He said that...

231
00:22:13,598 --> 00:22:15,867
you were my assistant in the kitchen.

232
00:22:16,335 --> 00:22:18,537
You make great international food,

233
00:22:19,471 --> 00:22:20,639
as for me,

234
00:22:21,773 --> 00:22:23,709
I make Thai food and Chinese food.

235
00:22:27,646 --> 00:22:28,914
Anything else?

236
00:22:29,481 --> 00:22:32,484
You are a friend he loves dearly.

237
00:22:34,319 --> 00:22:35,153
And you...

238
00:22:36,121 --> 00:22:37,923
also love me very much.

239
00:22:41,126 --> 00:22:43,762
So what are you doing now?

240
00:22:44,896 --> 00:22:45,964
I'm drawing.

241
00:22:48,567 --> 00:22:50,068
You want me to hang out here with you?

242
00:22:53,605 --> 00:22:54,373
It's okay.

243
00:22:59,478 --> 00:23:02,481
Okay. See you soon, then!

244
00:24:53,692 --> 00:24:55,026
I've come to pay my respects to you.

245
00:24:55,994 --> 00:24:58,396
I apologize for coming so late.

246
00:24:59,431 --> 00:25:03,768
I don't know...if I came here earlier, would you have helped me achieve my wishes in love.

247
00:25:05,370 --> 00:25:07,405
But if I asked you to help me now,

248
00:25:08,106 --> 00:25:09,307
would you help me?

249
00:25:29,427 --> 00:25:30,428
A person like you...

250
00:25:31,162 --> 00:25:32,797
believes in Holy Power too?

251
00:25:34,366 --> 00:25:35,200
What about you?

252
00:25:36,268 --> 00:25:37,769
Did you get anything you asked for?

253
00:25:38,370 --> 00:25:40,071
I asked for Tao Sor to come back.

254
00:25:44,175 --> 00:25:45,377
I won't ask the gods for anything.

255
00:25:48,513 --> 00:25:50,415
But there's something I want to ask from you.

256
00:25:56,788 --> 00:25:58,657
In a few days, I'll be going back to Bangkok.

257
00:26:00,025 --> 00:26:03,028
I want Tao Sor's cooking for my last meal here.

258
00:26:22,047 --> 00:26:23,281
Does it look good, Dad?

259
00:26:24,816 --> 00:26:25,884
It's so cute, Kim.

260
00:26:38,597 --> 00:26:39,965
Did you know?

261
00:26:41,266 --> 00:26:42,968
I love Southern Fish Curry!

262
00:26:43,068 --> 00:26:44,469
Southern Fish Curry?

263
00:26:45,136 --> 00:26:46,638
When did you start liking this?

264
00:26:46,771 --> 00:26:50,208
I've known you all your life, I've never seen you eat this.

265
00:26:50,775 --> 00:26:52,177
Someone showed me how to eat it.

266
00:26:52,844 --> 00:26:54,713
Someone showed you?

267
00:26:54,879 --> 00:26:56,715
Wait till you see my dish!

268
00:27:01,653 --> 00:27:03,121
Happy Birthday, bro!

269
00:27:03,488 --> 00:27:09,227
Hope you stay handsome, get richer, and finally find true love.

270
00:27:14,532 --> 00:27:15,734
That might be a bit hard.

271
00:27:16,401 --> 00:27:17,669
Once I'm back in Bangkok,

272
00:27:18,970 --> 00:27:20,972
would I be able to find anyone?

273
00:27:24,676 --> 00:27:25,677
You find someone.

274
00:27:29,047 --> 00:27:30,248
How's the food?

275
00:27:31,116 --> 00:27:32,283
We haven't had any yet.

276
00:27:32,751 --> 00:27:34,352
Everything looks really good!

277
00:27:37,555 --> 00:27:38,723
Thank you, Talay!

278
00:27:39,290 --> 00:27:40,925
Once I'm back in Bangkok...

279
00:27:42,594 --> 00:27:44,596
I'm gonna miss Phuket food to death.

280
00:27:46,431 --> 00:27:47,599
Enjoy your meal.

281
00:27:49,034 --> 00:27:52,337
Happy Birthday to you,

282
00:27:52,804 --> 00:27:56,841
Happy Birthday to you,

283
00:28:04,115 --> 00:28:06,051
Make a wish, Sir.

284
00:28:23,468 --> 00:28:24,469
Tao Sor.

285
00:28:24,836 --> 00:28:25,870
Go home.

286
00:28:27,672 --> 00:28:29,007
You wanna go running today?

287
00:28:29,908 --> 00:28:31,509
Can we do something else?

288
00:28:59,771 --> 00:29:00,472
I'm sorry.

289
00:29:01,573 --> 00:29:04,642
It's okay. I'll have someone clean this up.

290
00:29:15,687 --> 00:29:16,755
Thank you.

291
00:29:27,999 --> 00:29:29,367
Please excuse me.

292
00:29:29,667 --> 00:29:30,802
Thank you..

293
00:29:36,775 --> 00:29:38,076
I don't have a fork.

294
00:29:40,512 --> 00:29:41,412
Here.

295
00:32:43,928 --> 00:32:47,031
Kim, there's another tour for Wat Arun booked for today.

296
00:32:47,031 --> 00:32:49,534
But all the guides are busy, will you take them yourself?

297
00:32:52,136 --> 00:32:54,005
Tell them that we're fully booked for today,

298
00:32:54,572 --> 00:32:56,708
If they want to go, they'll have to book for tomorrow.

299
00:32:57,175 --> 00:32:58,109
Okay.

300
00:33:08,119 --> 00:33:10,888
Kim, shall we go have Phuket food for dinner tonight?

301
00:33:11,155 --> 00:33:13,358
I know that you miss Phuket.

302
00:33:16,394 --> 00:33:17,228
Sure, Mom.

303
00:33:17,795 --> 00:33:19,931
You want to try arranging new trips?

304
00:33:20,732 --> 00:33:24,936
When you were in Phuket, your uncle wouldn't stop complimenting you.

305
00:33:27,972 --> 00:33:29,240
I'd rather not, Mom.

306
00:33:29,674 --> 00:33:32,677
I'm already overwhelmed with the work as is!

307
00:33:32,977 --> 00:33:34,879
Okay, I won't disturb you any longer.

308
00:33:49,594 --> 00:33:51,229
Hello? What's up, Siw?

309
00:33:51,462 --> 00:33:53,765
Someone misses your 1 Day Trip.

310
00:33:56,200 --> 00:33:56,968
Who?

311
00:33:57,769 --> 00:34:00,171
Nao. Who'd you think it was?

312
00:34:03,074 --> 00:34:03,708
Well...

313
00:34:04,542 --> 00:34:05,843
I wasn't thinking of anyone.

314
00:34:06,244 --> 00:34:08,946
Don't play dumb. We're all grown ups here.

315
00:34:10,415 --> 00:34:11,482
So...

316
00:34:12,283 --> 00:34:14,719
by the way, have you been to that resort lately?

317
00:34:15,153 --> 00:34:19,090
Since the day we sent you off, I haven't been back there at all.

318
00:34:20,358 --> 00:34:23,928
Kim, you don't have to keep pushing down the things you don't forget.

319
00:34:24,228 --> 00:34:25,730
Weren't you the one who said that?

320
00:34:30,368 --> 00:34:33,371
I'll go visit when I have time, okay?

321
00:34:33,838 --> 00:34:35,073
Hurry back!

322
00:34:35,306 --> 00:34:38,476
I think there might be someone waiting for you.

323
00:34:43,648 --> 00:34:45,083
He...

324
00:34:46,050 --> 00:34:49,053
might..not remember anything at all.

325
00:34:50,455 --> 00:34:51,722
Oh, Kim.

326
00:34:52,890 --> 00:34:54,192
Don't think like that.

327
00:34:57,528 --> 00:34:58,463
That's all.

328
00:34:59,464 --> 00:35:01,332
Oay, Kim. See you!

329
00:35:21,752 --> 00:35:24,355
Wait here, Tao Sor. I'm gonna go to the bathroom.

330
00:35:25,123 --> 00:35:25,690
Okay.

331
00:37:17,401 --> 00:37:18,669
Tao Sor!

332
00:38:08,452 --> 00:38:10,921
What's wrong? Why are you crying?

333
00:38:14,892 --> 00:38:15,960
Oh.

334
00:38:16,827 --> 00:38:17,628
It's nothing.

335
00:38:32,009 --> 00:38:32,710
Tao Sor!

336
00:38:33,244 --> 00:38:34,445
why did you do this?

337
00:38:35,212 --> 00:38:35,913
Let's go.

338
00:39:05,643 --> 00:39:06,510
Bro...

339
00:39:09,480 --> 00:39:11,248
I dreamt of a man...

340
00:39:14,885 --> 00:39:16,387
I don't know who he is...

341
00:39:20,758 --> 00:39:22,493
I hear his voice,

342
00:39:24,095 --> 00:39:25,396
see only his shadow,

343
00:39:26,230 --> 00:39:28,265
but it was so real.

344
00:39:32,670 --> 00:39:34,305
I know him, right?

345
00:39:37,675 --> 00:39:38,876
I give in, Tao Sor.

346
00:39:41,212 --> 00:39:42,880
I'll take you to see him.
